or below the information,

00:07:56.081 --> 00:07:59.517
can assist Deaf people to understand

00:07:59.518 --> 00:08:02.253
information
in their preferred language

00:08:02.254 --> 00:08:05.690
and make it easy English,
simplified English,

00:08:05.691 --> 00:08:08.418
rather than using too much jargon

00:08:10.996 --> 00:08:14.905
and highfalutin words,
because Deaf people

00:08:14.906 --> 00:08:17.806
might find that difficult to follow.

00:08:18.871 --> 00:08:21.911
Using accessible videos,

00:08:21.951 --> 00:08:26.645
using things like players,

00:08:27.446 --> 00:08:34.219
AblePlayer, Video.js,
or WordPress-compatible plugins.

00:08:36.355 --> 00:08:42.428
That will support transcripts
and easy playback controls,

00:08:45.764 --> 00:08:50.369
which makes it much easier
for Deaf people to navigate.

00:08:52.271 --> 00:08:57.795
Try to provide short video
explainers for key pages

00:08:59.602 --> 00:09:04.917
such as the homepage,
the contact page,

00:09:05.184 --> 00:09:08.754
and particular forms
that might be integrated.

00:09:10.189 --> 00:09:12.918
Otherwise, things
can be quite complicated

00:09:12.919 --> 00:09:15.068
and difficult to navigate.

00:09:17.396 --> 00:09:23.469
Fourthly, using picture-in-picture
split screen layouts,

00:09:25.738 --> 00:09:27.905
having things side by side.

00:09:27.906 --> 00:09:29.807
If there's a presenter,

00:09:30.576 --> 00:09:35.347
trying to put the Deaf interpreter
or the translator,

00:09:36.115 --> 00:09:39.671
whether they be a
hearing-translator/interpreter

00:09:39.672 --> 00:09:41.953
or Deaf interpreter, side by side,

00:09:41.954 --> 00:09:45.223
so it's very visually easy to glean

00:09:45.224 --> 00:09:47.869
the information by the audience,

00:09:49.528 --> 00:09:52.163
and it's easy to navigate as well.

00:09:52.164 --> 00:09:57.703
On my laptop,
whether I use a computer or an iPad,

00:09:57.803 --> 00:10:02.941
I make sure that the audience
can see me today,

00:10:03.509 --> 00:10:06.458
even though my laptop is different

00:10:06.459 --> 00:10:10.282
to what you're seeing on the screen.

00:10:11.917 --> 00:10:14.786
Deaf people and hearing people

00:10:14.787 --> 00:10:18.056
might be interpreters,
