00:10:18.057 --> 00:10:23.094
that they are framed correctly
so that it's very easy to understand

00:10:23.095 --> 00:10:26.903
the sign language,
and the hands are not cut off.

00:10:27.566 --> 00:10:29.797
There are particular themes

00:10:30.069 --> 00:10:32.714
that are accessible and plugins.

00:10:34.573 --> 00:10:38.744
You would need to select
WordPress themes

00:10:40.179 --> 00:10:41.858
that are compatible

00:10:41.859 --> 00:10:47.218
to (WCAG) 2.1 so they're compliant

00:10:47.219 --> 00:10:52.791
and they support the embedded
media without breaking the design,

00:10:54.293 --> 00:10:57.562
because if that design is broken,

00:10:57.563 --> 00:11:03.102
Deaf people will decide
perhaps not to engage.

00:11:04.770 --> 00:11:10.042
We want Deaf people
